snippet.title: Best VGM 2002 - The Elder Scrolls III : Morrowind - The Road Most Travelled
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1474 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MvJUxw8rbPA
Best VGM 2159 - https://youtu.be/DmpP-RMFNHo

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.
PC / Xbox
The Elder Scrolls III : Morrowind (2002)
The Road Most Travelled
Jeremy Soule
